OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFor many, it
OL,6,Fwill be a dry night with patchy cloud
OL,7,Fand clear spells. Cloudy with strong
OL,8,Fwinds over the Western Isles however
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA cloudy day, though a few
OL,12,Fbrighter spells in east where mainly
OL,13,Fdry. Outbreaks of rain over Western
OL,14,FIsles and parts of West Highland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
